Dialogue: 3,0:01:01.48,0:01:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 抱歉迟到了-没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.48,0:01:03.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sorry for being late - No, it's okay
Dialogue: 3,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么不点东西？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why didn't you order anything?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不 我没想到你会来所以
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No I didn't think you would be coming, so
Dialogue: 3,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是 我还是来了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yet here I am
Dialogue: 3,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不用了，谢谢，我什么都不要，请便吧
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, thank you I don't want anything Please go ahead
Dialogue: 3,0:01:13.64,0:01:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 确定?-是的 当然 请
Dialogue: 2,0:01:13.64,0:01:15.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sure? - Yes Sure Please
Dialogue: 3,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不好意思
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Excuse me
Dialogue: 3,0:01:20.72,0:01:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“所以，上次你拒绝和我说话”
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.72,0:01:22.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'So, the last time you refused to talk to me'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么改变了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'What changed?'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好奇，很好
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Curious Good
Dialogue: 3,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我对别的事情很好奇
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm curious about something else
Dialogue: 3,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们正在经历一场经济危机
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We were going through an economic crisis
Dialogue: 3,0:01:35.16,0:01:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府变了，首相也变了，一切都变了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.16,0:01:37.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Government changed, the prime minister changed Everything changed
Dialogue: 3,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是股票市场保持稳定，现在依然如此
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But the stock market remained stable And it still is
Dialogue: 3,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在暗示什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you trying to insinuate?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:46.28,0:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都在赚钱
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.28,0:01:47.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone is making a profit
Dialogue: 3,0:01:48.68,0:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是件好事
Dialogue: 2,0:01:48.68,0:01:49.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's a good thing
Dialogue: 3,0:01:50.12,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.12,0:01:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:51.28,0:01:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.28,0:01:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So
Dialogue: 3,0:01:53.16,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.16,0:01:54.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}you mean
Dialogue: 3,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔和他的追随者？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta and his followers?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在哈尔沙德•巴伊(Harshad Bhai)统治时期，市场变得疯狂
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'In Harshad Bhai's reign, the market goes insane'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能跟你说实话吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can I be honest with you?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不太喜欢梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not a very big fan of Mr Mehta
Dialogue: 3,0:02:05.44,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你就是个例外
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.44,0:02:06.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then you are an exception
Dialogue: 3,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为你们兄弟会的人
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because the people of your fraternity
Dialogue: 3,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}宣称他是市场上最伟大的学者
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}have declared him the greatest scholar in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“有些人甚至认为他应该当财政部长”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'Some even think that he should be the finance minister'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生肯定能成为一名部长
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Mehta can surely become a minister
Dialogue: 3,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他总是发表演说
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is always delivering speeches
Dialogue: 3,0:02:21.12,0:02:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我个人认为他的理论都是垃圾
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.12,0:02:25.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I I personally, think his theories are just rubbish
Dialogue: 3,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没人在乎你我的想法
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nobody cares what you and I think
Dialogue: 3,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，资金正在流入市场
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right now, money is flowing into the market
Dialogue: 3,0:02:32.60,0:02:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都在这条河里游泳
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.60,0:02:34.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and everyone is taking a dip in this river
Dialogue: 3,0:02:35.20,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是没有人关心这条河的源头在哪里
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.20,0:02:37.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But no one cares where the source of this river is
Dialogue: 3,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些钱是从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where is all this money coming from?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道，很多人认为这是脏钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know, lots of people think it's the underworld?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:43.44,0:02:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毫无根据的理论
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.44,0:02:44.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Baseless theories
Dialogue: 3,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，这些资金来自哪里呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, where are the funds coming from?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:54.24,0:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德不需要黑社会
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.24,0:02:55.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad doesn't need
Dialogue: 3,0:02:55.92,0:02:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或政党资助他
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.92,0:02:59.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}the underworld or political parties to fund him
Dialogue: 3,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府在他的掌控之中
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has the government in his pocket
Dialogue: 3,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他打了一个电话，他在德里的朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He makes one phone call, and his friends in Delhi
Dialogue: 3,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}指示所有政府机构
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}instruct all government institutions
Dialogue: 3,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为他提供所有他想要的资金
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}to provide him with all the funds he wants
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有什么证据吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any proof for this?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有，但我很确定
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No But I know it for sure
Dialogue: 3,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}上次我试着联系你
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Last time, I tried to reach out to you
Dialogue: 3,0:03:26.16,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我正在写一篇关于货币市场违规现象的报道
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.16,0:03:28.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}because I was doing a story on the irregularities in the money market
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.76,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但你似乎只对哈尔沙德 · 梅塔感兴趣
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.76,0:03:32.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you seem to be interested only in Harshad Mehta
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.88,0:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.88,0:03:33.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为在货币市场也是，一切都乱套了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because in money market also, everything is going haywire
Dialogue: 3,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有的金融机构和银行都在哈沙德的控制之下
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the financial institutions and banks are under Harshad's control
Dialogue: 3,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他垄断了所有的证券，并在市场中占据了一席之地
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is cornering all the securities and taking positions in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:03:44.76,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.76,0:03:45.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right now
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}其他的都不重要
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}nothing else matters
Dialogue: 3,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是你的优点，不是你的技能，什么都不是
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not your merit, not your skill Nothing
Dialogue: 3,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}唯一重要的是
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The only thing that matters is
Dialogue: 3,0:03:53.64,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能贿赂这些银行官员多少钱
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.64,0:03:56.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}how much you can grease the palms of these bank officials
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为哈沙德很擅长这个
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because Harshad is very good at it
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他这样做了，所以我们也不得不这样做
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He does it, so we are also compelled to do it
Dialogue: 3,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们不能让银行官员满意
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we don't keep the bank officials happy
Dialogue: 3,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至都得不到我们所做的小生意
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}we won't even get the little business that we do
Dialogue: 3,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}上周，UCO 银行
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Last week, UCO Bank
Dialogue: 3,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给了哈尔沙德五亿卢比的纯信用贷款
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}gave Harshad a clean credit of fifty crores
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.28,0:04:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你了解信用贷款吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.28,0:04:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you understand clean credit?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不需要任何担保
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without any collateral
Dialogue: 3,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想让我为此写篇报道？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you want me to do a story on this?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以引用你的话吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can I quote you on this?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可以
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No
Dialogue: 3,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那就没有报道了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then there is no story
Dialogue: 3,0:04:34.36,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像你说的，没人在乎我们的想法
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.36,0:04:38.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As you said, nobody cares about what we think
Dialogue: 3,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我要刊登反对哈尔沙德先生的文章
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I have to print anything against Mr Harshad Mehta
Dialogue: 3,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那就需要确凿的证据
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}then I will need solid evidence
Dialogue: 3,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不能对他做任何事
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't do anything against him
Dialogue: 3,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我需要这些细节来揭露他的作案手法
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}because I will need those details to expose his modus operandi
Dialogue: 3,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will need something from you
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.12,0:04:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.12,0:04:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Fine
Dialogue: 3,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你很快就会得到确凿的证据
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You will get your solid evidence soon
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在我们进去之前，我想提醒你，我爸爸是个非常守旧的人
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Before we enter, I want to warn you that my dad is very old school
Dialogue: 3,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个难对付的家伙
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A hard nut to crack
Dialogue: 3,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道，他的观念非常传统
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is very, like you know, orthodox in his methods
Dialogue: 3,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Brother
Dialogue: 3,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管老派还是新派
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Old school or new school
Dialogue: 3,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}教学大纲都有一个共同的主题
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}every syllabus has one subject in common
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.08,0:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}利润
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.08,0:06:09.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Profit
Dialogue: 3,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是我最喜欢的科目
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that is my favourite subject
Dialogue: 3,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿姆里克告诉我，在你看来
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Amrik was telling me that in your opinion
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的公司被低估了？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}our company is undervalued?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，它被低估了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, it is undervalued
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.76,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是毫无疑问的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.76,0:06:20.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's no doubt about it
Dialogue: 3,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在上个季度，贵司赚了超过2亿卢比的利润
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In the last quarter, you earned a profit of more than 20 crores
Dialogue: 3,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是股息支付只有40% 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But the dividend payout against it is only 40 percent
Dialogue: 3,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每股收益只有727卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'And earning per share is just 727 rupees'
Dialogue: 3,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我研究贵公司的财务状况已有一段时间了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have been studying your company's finances for a while
Dialogue: 3,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}目前的股价是多少? 22-23？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is the current value of your share? 22-23?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}接近28
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It touched 28
Dialogue: 3,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}差不多
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Same thing Same range
Dialogue: 3,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}到年底你预计股价达到多少？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And where do you intend to go by the year-end?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至少翻一倍
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Minimum double
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.08,0:06:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我相信，我可以把你们公司的股价提高到400
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.08,0:06:56.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe, I can take your company's share up to 400
Dialogue: 3,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花言巧语，我以前听过
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[scoffs] - Plain rhetoric I've heard this before
Dialogue: 3,0:07:04.64,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说你低估了公司的价值
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.64,0:07:07.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, when I said that you are undervaluing your company
Dialogue: 3,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}what I meant is
Dialogue: 3,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不应该仅仅根据收入来评价你的公司
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that you should not value your company only on the basis of what it earns
Dialogue: 3,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我，你们什么时候开始做生意的？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me When did you commence your business?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1972年
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1972
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是19年，很长一段时间
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's 19 years Long time
Dialogue: 3,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你投入了很多
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've invested a lot
Dialogue: 3,0:07:27.64,0:07:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的激情，你的时间，所有那些不眠之夜
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.64,0:07:30.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Your passion, your time, all those sleepless nights'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}介意我站起来吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You mind if I get up?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-请便 -谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Please - Thanks
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，19年前，你投资了多少钱来建立这个公司？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, 19 years back, how much money did you invest to build this company?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天，用同样的金额，是否有可能建立一个类似的公司？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today, with the same amount, is it possible to build a similar company?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可能，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not possible, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，要建立一个像 Polo 这样的公司，你现在需要多少钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, to build a company like Polo, how much money would you need today?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这才是你公司的真正价值所在
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now that's the real value of your company
Dialogue: 3,0:08:03.84,0:08:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真正的价值
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.84,0:08:04.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The true value
Dialogue: 3,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我称之为重置成本理论
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I call it my replacement cost theory
Dialogue: 3,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}以 ACC 的股票为例
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Take the example of ACC shares
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股价曾经是300
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was at 300
Dialogue: 3,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那今天呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And today?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}三千
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Three thousand
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看，在股票市场上，有些人相信命运
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, in the share market, some people believe in fate
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我只相信价值
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}but I only believe in value
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}据我所知
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And from what I understand
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你公司的价值比你想象的要高得多
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}the value of your company is much higher than you think
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.12,0:08:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不确定你的方法是否合法
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.12,0:08:41.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not sure if your methods are legitimate
Dialogue: 3,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在股票市场，一切都是合法的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In the share market, everything is legitimate
Dialogue: 3,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的方法是新的，非传统的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My methods are new, unconventional
Dialogue: 3,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以人们觉得是非法的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}so, people find them illegitimate
Dialogue: 3,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这对你有什么好处？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's in it for you?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一部分股权
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A part Stakes
Dialogue: 3,0:08:54.08,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}多少？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.08,0:08:54.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很大一部分
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sizeable
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Mehta
Dialogue: 3,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不久之前
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}some time back
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你控股了马自达
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}you had acquired Mazda
Dialogue: 3,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我白手起家建立了这个公司
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have built this company on my own
Dialogue: 3,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我仍然想拥有它
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and I still want to own it
Dialogue: 3,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你误会了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are misunderstanding
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想要股权并不意味着我想接管你的公司
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wanting a stake, doesn't mean I want to take over your company
Dialogue: 3,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的工作是创造财富
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I am in the business of creating wealth
Dialogue: 3,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我对卖钢铁不感兴趣
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not interested in selling steel
Dialogue: 3,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是你的专长
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's your expertise
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我甚至不想要董事会席位
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't even want a position on your board
Dialogue: 3,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有看上你的公司
Dialogue: 2,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not eyeing your company
Dialogue: 3,0:09:29.56,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 但我-对它的真正价值感兴趣
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.56,0:09:32.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But I'm - Interested in its real value
Dialogue: 3,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你懂我
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There you are
Dialogue: 3,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就杵在那不说话吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Will you just stand there or ask what's on your mind?
