Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What question?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.96,0:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}上次的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.96,0:19:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The usual
Dialogue: 3,0:19:10.76,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些资金将从哪里来
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.76,0:19:11.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘Where will the funds come from?'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.24,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道你能应付
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.24,0:19:13.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know you will manage
Dialogue: 3,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不用告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and you won't even tell me
Dialogue: 3,0:19:16.52,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是在你做任何事情之前都要三思，不要冲动
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.52,0:19:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But think before you do anything Don't be impulsive
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}西塔拉曼先生
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Sitaraman
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.16,0:19:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请坐
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.16,0:19:35.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have a seat
Dialogue: 3,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好吗? 一切都好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How are you? All well?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}咖啡？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Coffee?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不用，先生，我刚喝了咖啡
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, sir I just had coffee
Dialogue: 3,0:19:43.08,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.08,0:19:43.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.72,0:19:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你带来了价值五十亿卢比的支票
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.72,0:19:47.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have brought cheques worth 500 crores
Dialogue: 3,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have, haven't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那为什么不愿意喝100卢比的咖啡呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then why shy away from a 100 rupee coffee? Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:54.84,0:19:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.84,0:19:55.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Brother
Dialogue: 3,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给他一杯浓咖啡，我要茶
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A strong coffee for sir, and tea for me
Dialogue: 3,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}49.9亿，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}499, Sir
