Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- All signed - Great
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir
Dialogue: 3,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 先生-什么事？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sir - Yes?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我什么时候能拿到SGL？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When will I get SGL for it, sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:26.48,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有的
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.48,0:20:27.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Never
Dialogue: 3,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁还在用SGL？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who gives SGL these days?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我给你BRs，好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll give you BRs Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别这么紧张，兄弟，你已经把它交给我了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't get so tense, brother You've handed it to me now
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}风险已经转移到我身上了，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't this tension, that I'm taking from you?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且，我也不打算把它保留太久
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And, I don't intend to keep it for long
Dialogue: 3,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就这几天而已
Dialogue: 2,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's only a matter of a few days
Dialogue: 3,0:20:45.92,0:20:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，SGL 我的意思是，一旦我得到 BRs
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.92,0:20:50.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, Sir, the SGL I mean once I get the BRs
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要在账本上做记录
Dialogue: 2,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need to make entries in the books
Dialogue: 3,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再过几天
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sitaraman] 'Then after a few days'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要统计 PDO 的账目
Dialogue: 2,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need to tally the books in PDO
Dialogue: 3,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有这些都需要几天时间，所以
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All this takes a few days So
Dialogue: 3,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}亲爱的，你担心得太多了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Darling, you worry too much
Dialogue: 3,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是我与 SBI 的第一笔交易吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is this my first deal with SBI?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这次是一大笔钱
Dialogue: 2,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, this time, it's a big amount
Dialogue: 3,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有印度储备银行的指导方针，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the RBI guidelines, sir
Dialogue: 3,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在你的脑海里，你已经把这点钱想了珠穆朗玛峰
Dialogue: 2,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have turned this tiny amount to Mount Everest in your mind
Dialogue: 3,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“对我来说，每一笔钱都很少”
Dialogue: 2,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'For me, every amount is small'
Dialogue: 3,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过几天你就能拿到钱，到时候你就可以入账了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You'll get the money in a few days You can do the entry then
Dialogue: 3,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，如果金额很大
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, if the amount is big
