Dialogue: 2,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll buy a few shares in your wife's name
Dialogue: 3,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}希望你不介意
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope that's okay
