Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.12,0:21:40.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}we gave strict instructions to these banks
Dialogue: 3,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}严格遵守印度储备银行的准则
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}to strictly follow the RBI guidelines
