Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}主席先生，请看一下 SBI 的报告
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, please take a look at SBI's report
Dialogue: 3,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有什么特别的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anything specific?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:57.76,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我不知道他们这些天是怎么做证券交易的？
