Dialogue: 2,0:27:26.48,0:27:27.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Coward
Dialogue: 3,0:27:28.00,0:27:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把你的勇气藏在两腿之间是不会有任何结果的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:28.00,0:27:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hiding your courage between your legs won't get you anywhere
Dialogue: 3,0:27:30.56,0:27:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你得把勇气挂在胸前
Dialogue: 2,0:27:30.56,0:27:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have to pin it on your chest
Dialogue: 3,0:27:33.04,0:27:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的成语和谚语用完了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:33.04,0:27:34.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you done with your idioms and proverbs?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:35.04,0:27:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们现在可以谈生意了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:35.04,0:27:36.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can we talk business now?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:36.72,0:27:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}星期天有什么生意？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:36.72,0:27:37.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What business on a Sunday?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:38.56,0:27:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场上每个人都在谈论
Dialogue: 2,0:27:38.56,0:27:40.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone is talking in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:27:41.36,0:27:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的合伙人必须知道
Dialogue: 2,0:27:41.36,0:27:42.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your partner has to listen to it
Dialogue: 3,0:27:42.96,0:27:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁跟阿什温说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:42.96,0:27:44.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who said anything to Ashwin Bhai?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:45.68,0:27:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿
Dialogue: 2,0:27:45.68,0:27:46.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey
Dialogue: 3,0:27:47.48,0:27:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说的合伙人是我自己
Dialogue: 2,0:27:47.48,0:27:48.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm talking about myself
Dialogue: 3,0:27:53.96,0:27:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续，你听到了什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:53.96,0:27:55.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on now What did you hear?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:56.80,0:27:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Polo
Dialogue: 2,0:27:56.80,0:27:57.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Polo
Dialogue: 3,0:27:58.52,0:28:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大家都说你在操纵价格
Dialogue: 2,0:27:58.52,0:28:00.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone is saying that you are rigging the price
Dialogue: 3,0:28:01.16,0:28:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们要求进行调查
Dialogue: 2,0:28:01.16,0:28:02.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are asking for an inquiry
Dialogue: 3,0:28:03.48,0:28:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁是‘每个人’ ？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:03.48,0:28:04.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who is ‘everyone'?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:04.92,0:28:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场上所有的大玩家
Dialogue: 2,0:28:04.92,0:28:07.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the big players in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:28:07.72,0:28:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马努的军队
Dialogue: 2,0:28:07.72,0:28:08.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Manu Bhai's troops
Dialogue: 3,0:28:09.36,0:28:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}整个熊队
Dialogue: 2,0:28:09.36,0:28:10.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The entire bear gang
Dialogue: 3,0:28:10.84,0:28:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果这还不够的话，还有PMS也是如此
Dialogue: 2,0:28:10.84,0:28:13.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if that wasn't enough, the PMS investors too
Dialogue: 3,0:28:15.56,0:28:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该死
Dialogue: 2,0:28:15.56,0:28:16.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bloody hell
Dialogue: 3,0:28:17.76,0:28:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经把他们的投资翻了一番
Dialogue: 2,0:28:17.76,0:28:19.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have doubled all their investments
Dialogue: 3,0:28:19.96,0:28:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}熊队能做到吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:19.96,0:28:22.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can the bear gang do that?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:22.96,0:28:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}多亏了我，每个人的钱包都装满了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.96,0:28:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thanks to me, everyone has filled their vaults
Dialogue: 3,0:28:24.96,0:28:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在他们却开始玷污我的名声！
Dialogue: 2,0:28:24.96,0:28:26.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And now they are tarnishing my name M**********rs!
Dialogue: 3,0:28:27.20,0:28:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，这关系到你的名誉，明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:27.20,0:28:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes It's your reputation at stake Got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:31.20,0:28:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都突然变得勇敢起来
Dialogue: 2,0:28:31.20,0:28:33.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone has suddenly become brave
Dialogue: 3,0:28:36.72,0:28:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来，吃个咖喱角
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.72,0:28:37.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Here Have a Samosa
Dialogue: 3,0:28:42.48,0:28:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿着这个
Dialogue: 2,0:28:42.48,0:28:43.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hold this
Dialogue: 3,0:28:58.48,0:28:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你吃咖喱角
Dialogue: 2,0:28:58.48,0:28:59.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You eat the Samosa
Dialogue: 3,0:29:09.68,0:29:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}设计是你的专长，我不懂
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.68,0:29:12.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Designing is your department I won't understand it
Dialogue: 3,0:29:13.16,0:29:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对我来说，信息更重要
Dialogue: 2,0:29:13.16,0:29:14.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For me, the message is more important
Dialogue: 3,0:29:16.12,0:29:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，我想在市场上澄清我对Polo的立场
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.12,0:29:18.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, I want to clear my position on Polo in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:29:20.12,0:29:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我为我的投资者赚了很多钱
Dialogue: 2,0:29:20.12,0:29:22.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have earned a lot of money for my investors
Dialogue: 3,0:29:22.60,0:29:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比我承诺的要多得多
Dialogue: 2,0:29:22.60,0:29:24.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A lot more than what I promised
Dialogue: 3,0:29:25.28,0:29:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想让人们知道这一点
Dialogue: 2,0:29:25.28,0:29:26.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want the people to know this
Dialogue: 3,0:29:27.20,0:29:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，我在工作
Dialogue: 2,0:29:27.20,0:29:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see I'm working
Dialogue: 3,0:29:28.52,0:29:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让这个国家的人民更加繁荣
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.52,0:29:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}towards making the people of this country more prosperous
Dialogue: 3,0:29:32.28,0:29:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且，高摩正以其敏锐的商业头脑和诚信的品牌打入市场
Dialogue: 2,0:29:32.28,0:29:35.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Growmore is playing the market with business acumen and honesty
Dialogue: 3,0:29:35.80,0:29:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，诚信是关键词
Dialogue: 2,0:29:35.80,0:29:37.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, honesty is the key word
Dialogue: 3,0:29:38.00,0:29:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想直接对公众发表演讲
Dialogue: 2,0:29:38.00,0:29:40.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I want to speak to the public directly
Dialogue: 3,0:29:40.20,0:29:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想告诉他们
Dialogue: 2,0:29:40.20,0:29:41.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want to reach them
Dialogue: 3,0:29:42.64,0:29:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，应该怎么做？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:42.64,0:29:44.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, what do they call it?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:44.88,0:29:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}新闻稿
Dialogue: 2,0:29:44.88,0:29:45.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Press note
Dialogue: 3,0:29:46.08,0:29:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这么说吧，这是一个广告形式的新闻
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.08,0:29:48.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let’s say, it's a press note turned into an advertisement
Dialogue: 3,0:29:48.84,0:29:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可以用你的照片吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:48.84,0:29:51.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can we use your face?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:51.60,0:29:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是，我们可以把你的照片放到我们的报道中吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:51.60,0:29:54.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, can we put your face in our campaigns?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:56.60,0:29:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我又不是阿米塔布·巴沙坎，你却想用我的照片
Dialogue: 2,0:29:56.60,0:29:58.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I am no Amitabh Bachchan, that you want to use my face
Dialogue: 3,0:29:59.88,0:30:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，公众是这么认为的
Dialogue: 2,0:29:59.88,0:30:01.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, that's what the public thinks
Dialogue: 3,0:30:01.80,0:30:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是这个市场的阿米塔布·巴沙坎
Dialogue: 2,0:30:01.80,0:30:03.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that you are the Amitabh Bachchan of this market
Dialogue: 3,0:30:05.40,0:30:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[拉塔]“先生，人们是在质疑你，不是在质疑高摩资本”
Dialogue: 2,0:30:05.40,0:30:07.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Lata] 'Sir, people are questioning you, not Growmore'
Dialogue: 3,0:30:07.72,0:30:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要你的脸，因为你就是那张脸
Dialogue: 2,0:30:07.72,0:30:10.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And we want your face because you are the face
Dialogue: 3,0:30:17.08,0:30:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，继续
Dialogue: 2,0:30:17.08,0:30:18.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay Go ahead
Dialogue: 3,0:30:20.04,0:30:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让广告看起来像报纸上的文章
Dialogue: 2,0:30:20.04,0:30:21.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Make the ad look like a newspaper article
Dialogue: 3,0:30:22.96,0:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}标题应该是 
Dialogue: 2,0:30:22.96,0:30:24.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the headline should be
Dialogue: 3,0:30:24.76,0:30:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德·梅塔是个清白的人
Dialogue: 2,0:30:24.76,0:30:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta is a clean man
Dialogue: 3,0:30:26.96,0:30:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[拉塔]“这太直接了”
Dialogue: 2,0:30:26.96,0:30:27.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Lata] 'That is too direct'
Dialogue: 3,0:30:28.76,0:30:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，没人会在乎
Dialogue: 2,0:30:28.76,0:30:29.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nobody cares, actually
Dialogue: 3,0:30:30.60,0:30:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错，没人在乎
Dialogue: 2,0:30:30.60,0:30:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's true Nobody cares
Dialogue: 3,0:30:33.20,0:30:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}交给他们好了，报纸会刊登这样一个标题：
Dialogue: 2,0:30:33.20,0:30:35.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, left to them, the newspapers will print a headline
Dialogue: 3,0:30:36.80,0:30:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德·梅塔是个骗子
Dialogue: 2,0:30:36.80,0:30:38.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta is a liar
Dialogue: 3,0:30:41.60,0:30:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看这个
Dialogue: 2,0:30:41.60,0:30:42.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Read
Dialogue: 3,0:30:43.04,0:30:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我从一开始就知道
Dialogue: 2,0:30:43.04,0:30:44.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I knew it from the start
Dialogue: 3,0:30:45.08,0:30:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是个骗子
Dialogue: 2,0:30:45.08,0:30:46.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that you are a liar
Dialogue: 3,0:30:47.32,0:30:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是个骗子
Dialogue: 2,0:30:47.32,0:30:48.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta is a liar
Dialogue: 3,0:30:50.00,0:30:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好，现在报纸上都登了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:50.00,0:30:51.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good It's even out in the paper now
Dialogue: 3,0:30:52.88,0:30:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我对你撒了什么谎？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:52.88,0:30:54.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What lie did I tell you?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:54.80,0:30:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真要说吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:54.80,0:30:55.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:56.08,0:30:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我全都列出来，清单一定比证交所的还长
Dialogue: 2,0:30:56.08,0:30:59.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I start making a list, even my list will be included in the BSE listing
Dialogue: 3,0:31:00.20,0:31:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你答应我去美国，然而实际上连阿姆雷利（印度城市）都没去过
Dialogue: 2,0:31:00.20,0:31:02.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You promised America and didn't even take me to Amreli
Dialogue: 3,0:31:04.44,0:31:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我们去了欧洲，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:04.44,0:31:06.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we went to Europe, didn't we?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:07.52,0:31:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}假期来了，我们也要去美国
Dialogue: 2,0:31:07.52,0:31:09.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And let the vacations come, we'll go to America too
Dialogue: 3,0:31:10.28,0:31:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们要去的话，现在就要开始计划
Dialogue: 2,0:31:10.28,0:31:12.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we have to go, we need to start planning now
Dialogue: 3,0:31:12.76,0:31:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则就别去了
Dialogue: 2,0:31:12.76,0:31:13.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or else, forget about it
Dialogue: 3,0:31:14.32,0:31:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以这次你来制定计划，剩下的我来处理
Dialogue: 2,0:31:14.32,0:31:16.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So this time, you make the plan I'll manage the rest
Dialogue: 3,0:31:17.04,0:31:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你确定？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:17.04,0:31:17.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:18.32,0:31:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 当然-以我发誓
Dialogue: 2,0:31:18.32,0:31:19.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sure - Swear on me
Dialogue: 3,0:31:20.48,0:31:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}首先，给我捏捏脚
Dialogue: 2,0:31:20.48,0:31:21.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}First, massage my legs
Dialogue: 3,0:31:23.52,0:31:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你不带我去
Dialogue: 2,0:31:23.52,0:31:24.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If it doesn't happen
Dialogue: 3,0:31:25.28,0:31:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会在孟买到处张贴标语
Dialogue: 2,0:31:25.28,0:31:27.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will put banners all over Bombay
Dialogue: 3,0:31:27.44,0:31:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德・梅塔是个骗子，你等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 2,0:31:27.44,0:31:29.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that Harshad Mehta is a liar Just you wait
Dialogue: 3,0:31:36.04,0:31:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看这个了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:36.04,0:31:36.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you read it?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:38.08,0:31:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是个骗子”
Dialogue: 2,0:31:38.08,0:31:39.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Harshad Mehta is a liar"
Dialogue: 3,0:31:41.00,0:31:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁会在报纸上刊登这样的东西？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:41.00,0:31:42.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who gets something like this printed in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:44.44,0:31:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是不是有点失控了？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:44.44,0:31:45.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't it getting out of hand?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:46.96,0:31:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看完了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:46.96,0:31:48.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you read the full ad?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:49.32,0:31:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}标题只是为了吸引注意力
Dialogue: 2,0:31:49.32,0:31:51.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The first line is only to grab attention
Dialogue: 3,0:31:52.36,0:31:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，下面写着哈尔沙德·梅塔是个骗子
Dialogue: 2,0:31:52.36,0:31:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, it says below, that Harshad Mehta is a liar
Dialogue: 3,0:31:55.16,0:31:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为他为投资者赚取的利润比他承诺的要多得多
Dialogue: 2,0:31:55.16,0:31:59.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}because he earned much bigger profits for his investors than he promised
Dialogue: 3,0:32:06.28,0:32:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温
Dialogue: 2,0:32:06.28,0:32:07.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin Bhai
Dialogue: 3,0:32:16.24,0:32:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德的这种勇气是从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:16.24,0:32:19.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where does Harshad get this courage from?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:20.76,0:32:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}非但没有在市场上澄清自己的立场
Dialogue: 2,0:32:20.76,0:32:23.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Instead of addressing the market and clearing his position
Dialogue: 3,0:32:24.00,0:32:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}反而在孟买到处张贴海报和宣传画
Dialogue: 2,0:32:24.00,0:32:26.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he has stuck himself on posters and cut-outs all over Bombay
Dialogue: 3,0:32:32.48,0:32:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}历史开启了新的篇章 
Dialogue: 2,0:32:32.48,0:32:34.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A new chapter has been added to history
Dialogue: 3,0:32:36.40,0:32:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}叫做哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:32:36.40,0:32:37.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}called Harshad Mehta
Dialogue: 3,0:32:41.24,0:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在我不只想要跑步，而是想起飞
Dialogue: 2,0:32:41.24,0:32:43.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now I don't just want to run, it's the time to leap
Dialogue: 3,0:32:45.36,0:32:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道阿什温不会理解的
Dialogue: 2,0:32:45.36,0:32:47.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know Ashwin Bhai won't understand this
Dialogue: 3,0:32:48.32,0:32:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是为什么你不能理解这些呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:48.32,0:32:50.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But why can't your brain process this?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:52.16,0:32:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场上的人不能做营销吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:52.16,0:32:54.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can't a person from the market do marketing?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:54.84,0:32:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:54.84,0:32:55.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hmm?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:56.92,0:32:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看这张脸
Dialogue: 2,0:32:56.92,0:32:57.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at this face
Dialogue: 3,0:32:59.40,0:33:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}仔细看
Dialogue: 2,0:32:59.40,0:33:00.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look carefully
Dialogue: 3,0:33:01.68,0:33:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它的面值就是我们的净资产
Dialogue: 2,0:33:01.68,0:33:03.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its face value is our net worth
Dialogue: 3,0:33:05.76,0:33:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想当英雄？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:05.76,0:33:06.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You want to be a hero?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:14.72,0:33:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道印度最大的制造业是什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:14.72,0:33:16.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know what India manufactures the most?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:18.60,0:33:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 水泥钢铁-英雄和神明
Dialogue: 2,0:33:18.60,0:33:20.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Cement, steel - Heroes and gods
Dialogue: 3,0:33:23.12,0:33:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天的平民可以成为明天的英雄
Dialogue: 2,0:33:23.12,0:33:25.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today's common man can be tomorrow's hero
Dialogue: 3,0:33:25.12,0:33:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天的英雄可以成为明天的上帝
Dialogue: 2,0:33:25.12,0:33:26.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today's hero can be tomorrow's God
Dialogue: 3,0:33:27.88,0:33:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}板球运动员，政客，电影明星 他们都这么做
Dialogue: 2,0:33:27.88,0:33:30.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Cricketers, politicians, film stars they all do this
Dialogue: 3,0:33:32.20,0:33:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，我们印度人喜欢创造英雄
Dialogue: 2,0:33:32.20,0:33:34.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Actually, we Indians love creating heroes
Dialogue: 3,0:33:36.32,0:33:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果人们觉得哈尔沙德 · 梅塔能给他们一个更光明的未来
Dialogue: 2,0:33:36.32,0:33:38.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If people feel Harshad Mehta can give them a brighter future
Dialogue: 3,0:33:38.96,0:33:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:38.96,0:33:39.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:40.68,0:33:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}越多的人拥护我们，我们就能更多地推动市场
Dialogue: 2,0:33:40.68,0:33:43.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}More the people that move towards us, the more we can move the market
Dialogue: 3,0:33:44.56,0:33:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，我不想去市场做演讲
Dialogue: 2,0:33:44.56,0:33:46.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, I don't want to go to the market and give a speech
Dialogue: 3,0:33:47.68,0:33:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想依靠人们的信任
Dialogue: 2,0:33:47.68,0:33:49.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want to rely on people's trust
Dialogue: 3,0:33:52.96,0:33:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这正是我想说的
Dialogue: 2,0:33:52.96,0:33:54.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's what I'm saying
Dialogue: 3,0:33:55.48,0:33:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要玩弄人们的信任
Dialogue: 2,0:33:55.48,0:33:57.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't play with people's trust
Dialogue: 3,0:34:19.68,0:34:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“这则广告对他产生了奇妙的效果”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:19.68,0:34:21.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] ‘The ad did wonders for him'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:22.44,0:34:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使人们认为哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是个骗子 
Dialogue: 2,0:34:22.44,0:34:24.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘Even if people thought Harshad Mehta was a liar'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:24.92,0:34:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也不在乎
Dialogue: 2,0:34:24.92,0:34:25.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘they didn't care'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:26.68,0:34:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有投资哈沙德股票的人都获利了
Dialogue: 2,0:34:26.68,0:34:30.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘All who invested in Harshad's shares, made a profit'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:30.96,0:34:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像 ACC、 Polo、马自达这样的公司股价暴涨
Dialogue: 2,0:34:30.96,0:34:34.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘The way the value of shares like ACC, Polo, Mazda was rising'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:34.96,0:34:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人能想象得到
Dialogue: 2,0:34:34.96,0:34:37.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘no one could have imagined it'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:37.68,0:34:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈萨德是新的市场领袖
Dialogue: 2,0:34:37.68,0:34:39.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘Harshad was the new market guru'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:39.84,0:34:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他无处不在
Dialogue: 2,0:34:39.84,0:34:41.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘He was everywhere'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:41.40,0:34:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经纪人、投资者、商人、政客 
Dialogue: 2,0:34:41.40,0:34:44.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘Brokers, investors, businessmen, politicians'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:44.28,0:34:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个男人都想成为哈沙德的特殊男人
Dialogue: 2,0:34:44.28,0:34:46.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘every man wanted to be Harshad's special man'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:46.72,0:34:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都想知道他的下一步计划是什么
Dialogue: 2,0:34:46.72,0:34:49.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘Everyone wanted to know what his next step would be'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:49.92,0:34:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，他现在对那些曾经垄断市场的
Dialogue: 2,0:34:49.92,0:34:54.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘And so, he was now a threat to those brokers and family-owned businesses'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:54.44,0:34:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经纪人和家族企业构成了威胁 
Dialogue: 2,0:34:54.44,0:34:56.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘who had monopolized the market so far'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:56.76,0:34:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人喜欢外人
Dialogue: 2,0:34:56.76,0:34:58.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘No one likes an outsider'
Dialogue: 3,0:35:46.68,0:35:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你整天向上帝祈祷，至少让他晚上睡个好觉
Dialogue: 2,0:35:46.68,0:35:49.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All day you pray to God At least, let him sleep at night
Dialogue: 3,0:35:51.16,0:35:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要说那样的话
Dialogue: 2,0:35:51.16,0:35:52.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't say things like that
Dialogue: 3,0:35:55.60,0:35:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想他最近都只回应你的祈祷
Dialogue: 2,0:35:55.60,0:35:57.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think he only answers your prayers these days
Dialogue: 3,0:36:02.16,0:36:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你儿子现在是全国最高级别的纳税人
Dialogue: 2,0:36:02.16,0:36:05.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your son is now the highest advance taxpayer in the country
Dialogue: 3,0:36:05.76,0:36:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至比迪鲁拜还要高
Dialogue: 2,0:36:05.76,0:36:06.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even higher than Dhirubhai
Dialogue: 3,0:36:08.52,0:36:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一定是因为上帝只听你的
Dialogue: 2,0:36:08.52,0:36:10.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This must be because he only listens to you
Dialogue: 3,0:36:18.76,0:36:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至少，双手合十拜一次
Dialogue: 2,0:36:18.76,0:36:20.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}At least, fold your hands once
Dialogue: 3,0:36:21.92,0:36:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这都是因为他的祝福
Dialogue: 2,0:36:21.92,0:36:23.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's all because of his blessings
Dialogue: 3,0:36:33.96,0:36:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}妈妈
Dialogue: 2,0:36:33.96,0:36:34.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mummy
Dialogue: 3,0:36:37.92,0:36:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看你儿子现在能打开多少扇门
Dialogue: 2,0:36:37.92,0:36:40.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just see, how many doors this Harshad Shantilal Mehta opens
Dialogue: 3,0:36:46.28,0:36:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的办公室永远不会关门
Dialogue: 2,0:36:46.28,0:36:47.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Our offices will never close
Dialogue: 3,0:37:02.08,0:37:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“我发现了哈沙德令人难以置信的一面”
Dialogue: 2,0:37:02.08,0:37:03.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'I found out something incredible about Harshad'
Dialogue: 3,0:37:03.56,0:37:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的吗? 你把我带到这个废墟就为了告诉我这个？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:03.56,0:37:07.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Seriously? To tell me that you've brought me to this ruin?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:07.84,0:37:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道吗，有时候我觉得你在背着我和哈沙德偷情
Dialogue: 2,0:37:07.84,0:37:10.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know, sometimes it feels that you are cheating on me with Harshad
Dialogue: 3,0:37:10.68,0:37:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么说? 他是我的第二任妻子吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:10.68,0:37:12.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do they say? Is he my second wife?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:13.24,0:37:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才不是，别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 2,0:37:13.24,0:37:15.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not called second wife Stop joking!
Dialogue: 3,0:37:15.40,0:37:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管怎样，你还记得马自达工业吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:15.40,0:37:17.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway, you remember Mazda industries?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:17.68,0:37:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去年我的第二任妻子收购的公司
Dialogue: 2,0:37:17.68,0:37:20.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Last year, my second wife bought it
Dialogue: 3,0:37:21.64,0:37:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}抱歉，你继续说
Dialogue: 2,0:37:21.64,0:37:22.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sorry Go on
Dialogue: 3,0:37:23.60,0:37:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的，哈尔沙德去年收购了 -对
Dialogue: 2,0:37:23.60,0:37:25.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes, Harshad bought it last year - Right
Dialogue: 3,0:37:25.84,0:37:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一家亏损的租赁公司
Dialogue: 2,0:37:25.84,0:37:27.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was a loss-making leasing company
Dialogue: 3,0:37:27.48,0:37:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}几个月后，哈尔沙德让这次收购看起来像是一个彻底的转折
Dialogue: 2,0:37:27.48,0:37:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and in a few months, Harshad made it seem like it was a complete turnaround
